messages.subject: Re: [Unschooling-dotcom] It's Nanci NOT Nancy AND Honesty
messages.msgSnippet: Nanci, hope the move goes well. I keep hoping for more people in my area that believe in unschooling. Not a lot in my neck of the woods. And sorry for the name
messages.messageBody:
Nanci,
hope the move goes well. I keep hoping for more people in my area that believe in unschooling. Not a lot in my neck of the woods. And sorry for the name spelling.
Johanna
Life is the ultimate learning experience!
----- Original Message -----
From: Nanci Kuykendall
To: Unschooling-dotcom@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Monday, April 30, 2001 9:33 AM
Subject: [Unschooling-dotcom] It's Nanci NOT Nancy AND Honesty


>Where you moving to Nancy, anywhere southern??

>Johanna
>Life is the ultimate learning experience!

Not picking on your Johanna, just wanted to clarify
for everyone. My name is Nanci, and there is at least
one Nancy on the list, so trying to keep us straight.

We are moving to the Pacific NW, in the Seattle Area,
most likely near Federal Way at first. We are working
on buildng an intentional community in that area (as
some of you know) and some of our community members
live in Federal Way, so we are trying to live close to
them before we buy land for our community.

Nanci K.
